MSP430 Infomemory Storage. More...

MSP430 Infomemory Storage.

Author:
Michael Baar <baar@inf.fu-berlin.de>

Functions to store and read data from the two infomemories (2 x 128 Bytes). Offset addresses start at zero, size has a maximum of 128, write operations across both blocks are not allowed.
